      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0646P0-06543'>
        <a name='S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_174'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-susan-miller' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_174' title='Link to this speech by Ms Susan Miller' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-susan-miller" title="Ms Susan Miller">Baroness Miller of Chilthorne Domer</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Clause 27 uses the words "serious damage", whereas in the <a href="/acts/environment-act-1995">Environment Act 1995</a> the words "significant damage" are used. Obviously the context is not exactly the same. Is the Minister confident that "serious damage" is adequately defined, or would "significant damage" achieve more efficiently the purpose sought of protecting those items that need protection?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0646P0-06544'>
        <a name='S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_175'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_175' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-whitty" title="Mr John Whitty">Lord Whitty</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The definitions of "serious damage" under this clause and elsewhere will be set out in detailed guidance. The assessment would be on that basis. Clearly, if the noble Baroness proposes an amendment, we shall have to deal with it at a later stage. We consider that the reference to "serious" indicates the type of damage of which we are talking, but it would be subject to guidance.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0646P0-06545'>
