          <p class='first-para'>
            Is it the case, then, that an ordinary court would not have powers to act sufficiently quickly? Is that the problem?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0646P0-06568'>
        <a name='S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_199'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_199' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
