      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0646P0-06673'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_304' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 36 [<span class="italic">Conditions relating to costs of water regulation</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0646P0-06674'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030403_GCR_305' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
